Python Data Structures for Humans

Generic, pure Python implementations of some more common types of data structures.


The list of data structures and algorithms can be found on this `this
<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_data_structures>`_. Wikipedia page


Release History
---------------
0.0.2 (2015-01-29)
++++++++++++++++++

* Added structs.arrays.ParallelArray
* Added structs.trees.base.Tree and structs.trees.base.Node
* Added structs.trees.binary.BinaryTree and structs.trees.binary.BinaryNode
* Added structs.trees.binary.BinarySearchTree

0.0.1 (2015-01-19)
++++++++++++++++++

* Initial conception/creation
